### Read classes
GET http://localhost:9000/classes

### Read class by id
GET http://localhost:9000/classes/50

### Read class students
GET http://localhost:9000/classes/1/students

### Create class
POST http://localhost:9000/classes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 50,
  "name": "hellezo23"
}

### Add a student to a class
POST http://localhost:9000/classes/1/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "stefan",
  "surname": "mir"
}

### Delete class
DELETE http://localhost:9000/classes/1

